title: #207: Cup o' Joe (@NickYoussef)
itunes:title: Cup o' Joe with Nick Youssef
description: Nick Youssef came to my hotel room in Seattle to talk about coffee. Nick has nothing of value in his life, so he fills his void by shopping for old records, thrift store clothes, and coffee. He's become kind of an afficianado. So we did a podcast all about the black art. We also talked about this sick fight we saw the night before on the streets.
